<section id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>
    The <strong>Foundation for Youth Advancement, Clarity and Transformation (F.A.C.T.)</strong> is an educational non-profit organization dedicated to empowering young people with knowledge, skills, and opportunities for personal and community growth.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="mission">
  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>
    To advance education and personal development by providing mentorship, skill-building programs, and resources that enable young people to thrive academically, professionally, and socially.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="programs">
  <h2>Our Programs</h2>
  <ul class="programs">
    <li>Educational workshops and seminars</li>
    <li>Youth mentorship and guidance</li>
    <li>Skill development and training sessions</li>
    <li>Community learning initiatives</li>
    <li>Digital education and technology awareness</li>
  </ul>
</section>

